<!-- ========================= SYSTEM DIAGRAM ========================= -->

<section id="diagram" class="card">
  <h2>System overview</h2>

  <div class="diagram">
    <pre><code>
DISCOVERY → VALIDATION → REFINEMENT → ARTIFACTS → TESTS → RELEASE SIGNAL

   DOM         pass/fail       scoped         JSON        Playwright     Gate
 extraction     check         locators       outputs        usage        decision
    </code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="callout">
    <span class="tag">Model</span>
    Locators are not authored — they are derived from the system, validated against reality,
    and refined until deterministic.
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ========================= DEFINITION OF DONE ========================= -->

<section id="done" class="card">
  <h2>Definition of done</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="ok">✔</span> Real page inventory generated from live system.</li>
    <li><span class="ok">✔</span> Locator candidates derived from accessibility semantics.</li>
    <li><span class="ok">✔</span> All locators validated (pass/fail recorded).</li>
    <li><span class="ok">✔</span> Ambiguity resolved via scoping or flagged.</li>
    <li><span class="ok">✔</span> Outputs stored as reusable artifacts.</li>
  </ul>
</section>


<!-- ========================= LOCATOR MODEL ========================= -->

<section id="priority" class="card">
  <h2>Locator priority model</h2>

  <table class="table">
    <tr>
      <td>Priority 1</td>
      <td><code>getByRole(role, &#123; name &#125;)</code></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Priority 2</td>
      <td><code>getByLabel()</code></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Priority 3</td>
      <td><code>getByPlaceholder()</code></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Priority 4</td>
      <td><code>getByText()</code></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Last resort</td>
      <td>CSS / XPath (HIGH risk)</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="callout">
    <span class="tag">Risk model</span>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>LOW:</strong> unique role + accessible name</li>
      <li><strong>MEDIUM:</strong> repeated names or dynamic text</li>
      <li><strong>HIGH:</strong> brittle selectors</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ========================= SYSTEM FLOW ========================= -->

<section id="flow" class="card">
  <h2>System flow</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Extract interactive elements from the DOM.</li>
    <li>Generate locator candidates.</li>
    <li>Validate each locator against the page.</li>
    <li>Refine ambiguous results.</li>
    <li>Persist outputs as artifacts.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="callout">
    <span class="tag">Key shift</span>
    The system replaces manual locator authoring with a deterministic pipeline.
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ========================= OPERATOR WORKFLOW ========================= -->

<section id="operator" class="card">
  <h2>Operator workflow</h2>

  <pre><code># Discover
node scripts/run-locator-extraction.js

# Validate
node scripts/validate-locators.js

# Refine
node scripts/generate-scoped-candidates.js</code></pre>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Valid:</strong> use in test</li>
    <li><strong>Invalid:</strong> apply scoped locator</li>
    <li><strong>Still failing:</strong> fix accessibility</li>
  </ul>
</section>


